news.title: Noida, Greater Noida authorities to take back plots lying unused for years
news.para: A notification issued by UP government in 2022 stated lease agreements of plots allotted to industrial, information technology and information technology-enabled units, which were not operational by December 31, 2022, will be revoked and e-auctioned to new investors.

news.title: CBI names Chintels India's CMD, seven more in Paradiso cave-in chargesheet
news.para: Two more Chintels executives, former CEO D Vasudevan and project manager Kuldeep Kumar Kaul, were charged by the CBI after a yearlong investigation since it took over the probe from Gurgaon police on January 17 last year.

news.title: NCR: Six builders made Rs 600 crore cash transactions to evade tax
news.para: Officials said the I-T teams recovered cash and jewellery worth over Rs 16 crore from their premises. Last Thursday, the I-T teams started its search operations at the six realty offices for alleged tax evasion.
